comments: Capela (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Holiday (MEM) and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Caboclo (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball during the drive by Harden (HOU).
Harden (HOU) establishes himself in a stationary position without delivering contact and Conley (MEM) initiates the contact attempting to contest the jump shot attempt.
RLB shows Capela (HOU) makes some contact with Holiday (MEM) during the rebound but does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
House Jr. (HOU) makes marginal contact with Caboclo (MEM) in transition but the contact does not affect his SQBR.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: The ball is last touched by Wright (MEM) prior to going out of bounds.
Capela (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Wright (MEM) and slightly extends his arm against him but he is able to move through the slight contact.
Harden (HOU) firms up and engages with Valanciunas (MEM) and the two players quickly disengage.
[Observable in enhanced video] Harden (HOU) moves his pivot foot prior to the start of his dribble.
House Jr. (HOU) slightly extends his arm against Conley (MEM) during the drive but he is able to continue defending the play.
Capela (HOU) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Paul (HOU) extends his leg on the jump shot attempt but the contact with Holiday (MEM) is marginal.
[Observable in enhanced video] Conley (MEM) moves his foot heel-to-toe to create space at the start of his dribble.
Valanciunas (MEM) firms up in a screening position in the path of Paul (HOU) and does not deliver contact.  The two players briefly engage and disengage when Valanciunas cuts to the basket.
Capela (HOU) makes marginal contact with Conley's (MEM) arm during the drive that does not affect his SQBR.
Paul (HOU) makes marginal contact to Conley's (MEM) arm during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Valanciunas (MEM) moves laterally into the path of Paul (HOU) at the end of the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Paul (HOU) makes marginal contact Wright (MEM) during the drive that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harden (HOU) and does not deliver the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Tucker (HOU) does not fully clear the lane and is standing on the lane line without actively guarding an opponent within three seconds.
Conley (MEM) makes marginal contact to House Jr.'s (HOU) arm that does not affect his control of the ball.
RAR shows Valanciunas (MEM) turns in mid-air and delivers contact to House Jr.'s (HOU) body during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Harden (HOU) wraps Conley (MEM) around the waist and affects his SQBR during the inbound.
Paul (HOU) commits a take foul on Caboclo (MEM).
Tucker (HOU) commits a take foul on Caboclo (MEM).
Noah (MEM) briefly puts an arm to Harden's (HOU) front following the pick but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Caboclo (MEM) legally contests Harden's (HOU) driving shot attempt.
RLB shows Holiday (MEM) makes contact with the ball and Capela (HOU) loses control of it.  The ensuing contact to Capela's arm is considered incidental.
[Observable in enhanced video] Capela (HOU) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
RLB shows Noah (MEM) jumps from point A to point B into Capela's (HOU) body prior to making contact with the ball and the body contact affects his play at the basket.
Paul (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Holiday (MEM) and slightly extends his arms during the screen but Holiday is able to move through the contact.
House Jr (HOU) commits a take foul on Holiday (MEM).
Tucker (HOU) briefly places an arm at Conley's (MEM) side but immediately removes it.
Holiday (MEM) makes contact to Harden's (HOU) head during his jump shot attempt.
Parson (MEM) loses control of the ball and when he regains possession, he maintains his pivot foot.
Tucker (HOU) makes incidental contact to the arm of Parsons (MEM) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Paul (HOU) is firming up in a legal picking position in Valanciunas's (MEM) path when contact occurs and he absorbs contact.
Valanciunas (MEM) briefly grasps Capela (HOU) but does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Caboclo (MEM) fails to fully clear the lane and is not actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Valanciunas (MEM) sets the pick in Paul's (HOU) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Valanciunas's (MEM) wrist and affects his ability to gather the rebound.
Tucker (HOU) is firming up in a legal picking position in Conley's (MEM) path when contact occurs and he absorbs contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Harden (HOU) has a foot in the lane without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Capela (HOU) sets the pick in Conley's (MEM) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Paul (HOU) firms up in a picking position in Wright's (MEM) path and absorbs contact.
Conley (MEM) legally contests Harden's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Valanciunas (MEM) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Harden (HOU) places a hand to Conley's (MEM) front and makes brief marginal contact at the start of the drive.
Video evidence is inconclusive whether Harden (HOU) makes contact with Conley's (MEM) head during his driving shot attempt.
Paul (HOU) establishes himself in a picking position in Wright's (MEM) path and absorbs contact.
Capela (HOU) extends his leg and intentionally kicks the ball during Wright's (MEM) dribble.
Valanciunas (MEM) sets the screen in Paul's (HOU) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Conley (MEM) makes inadvertent contact with Tucker (HOU) during the follow-through of his driving shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Paul (HOU) makes marginal contact with Conley's (MEM) body during his driving shot attempt.
